MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the SK9 postcode area of Wilmslow , affecting properties in Mossways Park and the surrounding area. Repairs are taking longer than expected because we need to replace broken overhead line equipment. Due to the complexity of the repairs required we now expect to have your supply restored by 3pm. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 10:38am on the 21st January 2021.
